    {9007,"Saving the Best for Last",60,1637,{"wago","emulator"},"A truly amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved, I can assure you. Through your efforts we are delivered from the mistakes of our past.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you have definitely earned and will truly enjoy.",nil,{16012},{{itemID=22109,count=1},{itemID=22113,count=1}},58,0,nil,"Give Mokvar your Wildheart Cowl and Wildheart Vest.",8,1024,178,nil,{16012}},
