    {9240,"Glacial Vest",60,3456,{"wago","emulator"},"Thanks to you and Omarion, may he rest in peace, I am now able to create a Glacial vest. All you need to do is bring me the materials and pay a small crafting fee.",nil,{16376},{{itemID=22652,count=1}},60,-3000000,nil,"Craftsman Wilhelm at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands wants 8 Frozen Runes, 8 Bolts of Runecloth, 6 Essences of Water, 4 Ironweb Spider Silks and 300 gold. You must also be of Exalted reputation with the Argent Dawn.",64,nil,255,nil,{16376}},
    {9241,"Polar Bracers",60,3456,{"wago","emulator"},"Thanks to you and Omarion (May he rest in peace), I am now able to create Polar bracers. All you need to do is bring me the materials and pay a small crafting fee.",nil,{16376},{{itemID=22663,count=1}},60,-2000000,nil,"Craftsman Wilhelm at Light's Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands wants 4 Frozen Runes, 12 Enchanted Leather, 3 Essence of Water, 3 Cured Rugged Hides and 200 gold. $B",64,nil,255,nil,{16376}},
